"SQL Query": SELECT FSID, UNIQUE_BYTES FROM `dedup_stats` GROUP BY FSID ORDER BY `dedup_stats`.`FSID` DESC
SELECT STGPOOL_NAME, TOTAL_SPACE_MB FROM `stgpools` WHERE TOTAL_SPACE_MB NOT LIKE '' GROUP BY STGPOOL_NAME ORDER BY `stgpools`.`STGPOOL_NAME`
SELECT NODEID, COUNT(NODEID) FROM `replicated_objects` GROUP BY NODEID
SELECT VOLID, SEGSIZE/1000000 from `af_segments` GROUP BY VOLID ORDER BY `af_segments`.`VOLID`
SELECT `nodes`.`NODENAME`, COUNT(`replicated_objects`.`NODEID`) FROM `replicated_objects` INNER JOIN `nodes` ON `replicated_objects`.`NODEID` = `nodes`.`NODEID` GROUP BY `replicated_objects`.`NODEID`
